                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable C</hi> 14.) I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction, which I got from Mr. Clark's office—(<hi rend="italic">read</hi>)—I was in the Court when he was tried—he is the same person.</p>
